  <h4>3. Add platform</h4>

  <p>You need to add platform SDK to the project to run on the simulator or device.</p>

  <pre>
  $ cd /path/to/the/project
  $ cordova platform add ios (or android)
  </pre>

  <h4>4. Run on the simulator</p>

  <p>Following command will run the application in the simulator.</p>

  <pre>
  $ cordova simulate
  </pre>

  <p>If the command fails, you are missing something. If you want a quicker solution, try Monaca with the following instruction.</p>
